Poor Charlie's Almanack
poor-charlies-almanack
Charlie Munger is an investment professional and long term partner of Warren Buffet. Two takeaways of from his life's work and this book in particular are: 1. Always look at the incentives. 2. Inverting a problem can be an important step for solving it.
